Well your new I can see ok well really just use google and type starting a server.

for owner go into your source and find data then click characters then find your name that you logged in with in game and change the player rights to 2.

for server name go into your client and find your client.java and search for the title of the server and change it to your liking…

if you did not understand what I just said please watch a tut…
